                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. James Carter and another. On 9th July we had forty yards of calico at our shop—I saw the prisoner stoop down, and walk away—a person came in and said, "A man has taken piece of calico from your shop door"—I went out and found the prisoner with it on his arm—it was my master's.</p>
